<seg id="203">6th Management of funds and state property</seg>
<seg id="204">6.1 Analysis of management</seg>
<seg id="205">In the Czech Republic, the approved budgeted expenditures of SUZ were increased by thirteen budgetary measures by CZK 103,077,000 in 2001.</seg>
<seg id="206">Of this, CZK 89 979 thousand (87.29%) were earmarked funds. Most of it was earmarked for dealing with the consequences of the Kosovo crisis (CZK 44,538 thousand) and ensuring health care provided to asylum seekers (CZK 38,870 thousand).</seg>
