<seg id="97">Price comparison of bridges and tunnels</seg>
<seg id="98">The two SAIs analysed the prices of bridges on the D8 and A17 motorways in order to identify bridges whose price was too high and to compare the prices of bridges on the German and Czech sides.</seg>
