<seg id="107">By far the most common type of construction were concrete bridges on both sides of the border (20 bridges on D 8, 36 bridges on A 17).</seg>
<seg id="108">The analysis focused mainly on this group of bridges, as the abundance of the set allowed the use of mathematical-statistical methods with a high degree of reliability of the results.</seg>
<seg id="109">The inspections revealed that the prices per m 2 of concrete bridges on both D 8 and A 17 depend on the size of the bridge (its length, area): the larger the bridge, the lower the price per m2 of the bridge structure.</seg>
